"title": "5742: wedding",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5742",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The public acknowledgment and celebration of a couple's marriage. The wedding followed betrothal and was a preliminary to sexual union. The occasion was marked by feasting, singing and rejoicing. The bride wore a wedding dress, jewellery and ornaments and both she and the groom were waited on by attendants.</p>\n<h2>Wedding garments</h2>\n<h3>The bride's wedding dress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:13\">PSA 45:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:65\">GEN 24:65</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:10\">EZK 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:7-Rev19:8\">REV 19:7–19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h3>The bride's jewellery and ornaments</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:18\">ISA 49:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:10\">ISA 61:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:32\">JER 2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:11-Ezek16:12\">EZK 16:11–16:12</a></p>\n<h2>Wedding festivities</h2>\n<h3>Weddings were occasions for rejoicing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:11\">JER 33:11</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:27-Gen29:28\">GEN 29:27–29:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:12\">JDG 14:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:11\">SNG 3:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:5\">ISA 62:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:34\">JER 7:34</a></p>\n<h3>Wedding songs</h3>\n<p>PSA 45:0, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:63\">PSA 78:63</a></p>\n<h3>The wedding banquet</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:10\">JDG 14:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:21-Gen29:22\">GEN 29:21–29:22</a> <em>A feast celebrates Jacob's wedding</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:2\">MAT 22:2</a> <em>a wedding banquet given by a king for his son</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:3-John2:10\">JHN 2:3–2:10</a> <em>Jesus Christ changes water into wine at a wedding feast</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:9\">REV 19:9</a> <em>the marriage supper of the Lamb</em></p>\n<h2>Guests and attendants at weddings</h2>\n<h3>Wedding guests</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:1-John2:2\">JHN 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:3-Matt22:10\">MAT 22:3–22:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:11-Matt22:12\">MAT 22:11–22:12</a> <em>Wedding guests were expected to wear appropriate clothes</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:8-Luke14:10\">LUK 14:8–14:10</a></p>\n<h3>Attendants on the groom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:29\">JHN 3:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:11\">JDG 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:20\">JDG 14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:15\">MAT 9:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:19\">MRK 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:34\">LUK 5:34</a></p>\n<h3>Bridesmaids</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:14\">PSA 45:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:1-Matt25:10\">MAT 25:1–25:10</a></p>\n<h2>Wedding gifts</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:16\">1KI 9:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:59\">GEN 24:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:24\">GEN 29:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:29\">GEN 29:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:14-Judg1:15\">JDG 1:14–1:15</a></p>\n<h2>Elements in the wedding ceremony</h2>\n<h3>Covering the bride</h3>\n<p>Sometimes the groom would cover the bride with his cloak as a symbol of protection:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:9\">RUT 3:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:8\">EZK 16:8</a></p>\n<h3>A covenanted commitment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:17\">PRO 2:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:14\">MAL 2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Blessing the couple</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:60\">GEN 24:60</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:11\">RUT 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>Consummating the marriage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:16\">JOL 2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:23\">GEN 29:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:5\">PSA 19:5</a></p>",
